    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<i><br>&quot;Imagine a world that defies the laws of space known to us. A world that is created by itself, by the will of nature, without the intervention of any man and other creatures. It breaks everything we know about mass and space. Elementary particles, gravity, geometry - all this works here not the way we used to.&quot;</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/df345a3f13a8454115ee6b6558237326.poster.avif?t=1768318234\" width=630 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/df345a3f13a8454115ee6b6558237326.webm?t=1768318234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/df345a3f13a8454115ee6b6558237326.mp4?t=1768318234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Density Limit</strong> is a cinematic investigation adventure game with an ordinary story in a surreal place. Your mission is to find out what happened here, why this space even exists and who’s to blame for the mess here.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the Unspace</h2>It's a whole new state-of-the-art world that was created by the nature itself with the help of the greatest minds. It has its own aesthetics and laws of geometry and physics. There is no upside or downside here, left is right and one step forward is one mile back. Forget about tryouts to make a map or to memorize the way back. The scientists tried to curb the Unspace and they paid a very high price.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/270c382550bd019b0bc3f2baa962a9bb.poster.avif?t=1768318234\" width=630 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/270c382550bd019b0bc3f2baa962a9bb.webm?t=1768318234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/270c382550bd019b0bc3f2baa962a9bb.mp4?t=1768318234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You're only a human</h2>This maze of concrete and glass had no builders. It was architected and designed by itself. You're just a detective and this is your crime scene.  <br>Your mission is to find out what is this place, what happened here and why does it even exists? So much questions, but you will not hear any answers, because witnesses are very far away, but on the other side of that wall at the same time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/6b9d0125540f1fd68d7f5dc095cd628a.poster.avif?t=1768318234\" width=630 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/6b9d0125540f1fd68d7f5dc095cd628a.webm?t=1768318234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2352390/extras/6b9d0125540f1fd68d7f5dc095cd628a.mp4?t=1768318234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
